source:  wasi-libc setjmp/longjmp support (wasm32), vendored verbatim.
         - setjmp.h      ← libc-top-half/musl/include/setjmp.h
         - bits/setjmp.h ← libc-top-half/musl/arch/wasm32/bits/setjmp.h
         - rt.c          ← libc-top-half/musl/src/setjmp/wasm32/rt.c
